reviews.text: Lunch there,  good food and reasonable price.

Food is good...you can try ochazute way to eat your dish with soup or tea on a bowl.. Difficult to catch a waiter. You can have some promotion with the shop nearby named hellolulu. Install the mall app named TOP (This is Our Place) to get points and redeem gifts
Decent food, comfy, kinda authentic. But staff attitude could have been better, which cost the final star

Decent comfy Japanese food at reasonable price. The atmosphere is quite homey too. Just that the waiters, who are mostly friendly, may seem to be rather rushing off during peak hours (which is kind of understandable).
Good value for money for lunch. Not the brightest service staff. Some were also kinda rude. Somewhat spacious but gets tricky when it’s a larger party. They can’t seem to cope.

Many restaurants in food court with different cuisine 
At affordable prices

Fun unique mall. Lots of cute themed characters around and the environment is very different from that of a typical mall. The stores here are more items based than clothing and are unique. Everything in here is more cartoon based.
Interesting mall tailored for young people.
This mall of many small shops mostly sells trivial souvenirs of nothing. This is not the place to go for anything practical. Useless distractions are not for those of a more puritanical disposition.

result.name: T.O.P This is Our Place

reviews.text:
鋪頭都幾多 同埋好多都係唔同種類
但好似唔多岩男仔
上次同男朋友行個陣
佢都話無咩岩佢
這個都算是新開的商場，在假日的時間，人流暢旺，特別是很多家傭流連的關係，女洗手間多人使用不在話下，連wi-fi 都無辦法連上，那麼~管理層便要想法子提升網絡容量！
彌敦道700號位於香港九龍旺角彌敦道700號，樓高23層，1984年至2015年由香港政府持有，2016年起由領展房地產投資信託基金持有。 項目於2018年6月開業，商場定名為T.O.P This is Our Place。商場位處旺角核心範圍，將以年輕、活力、動感及帶領潮流打造旺角地標。
應有盡有，接連旺角中心，方便購物。 值得一提係T.O.P有個放空空間， 唔落雨可以去坐吓，感覺舒服。

reviews.text: 今天下午來個早來的晚餐，食物質素還可以的，但是份量太「的骰」了，價錢是$79另加一，真是性價比低啊！

—
要咗牛肉壽喜燒定食($89)
有好多小砵 蔥同蛋都另上 自己落
配菜有南瓜嗰個ok 清湯個味怪怪哋

主角牛肉鍋個汁調較得唔錯
牛肉肥瘦適中 菇 豆腐都sok哂啲味

吉列炸蠔定食($79)
酥脆鹹香 碗飯可以再裝滿d

牛奶抹茶($29)
好澀好甘 好濃厚嘅抹茶味
如果唔鍾意咁澀 
可以食附上嘅石頭朱古力中和下
————————————————————
有加一服務費
紅葉茶屋
旺角彌敦道700號T.O.P This Is Our Place 3樓309-310號舖
有水準但唔夠人手。上菜時間有啲慢，可能多人。 今次我地試左滑旦豬扒飯，旦好味，豬扒鞋口，唔脆。差少少，仲有跟啲配菜咁。 中午時間無午餐，要加8元先有熱飲，加$10 有凍飲
牛肉壽喜燒定食👍🏼👍🏼
環境舒適， 食物份量比較細，但味道不錯❤️
